# Developer-local uv lockfile. orchestrator-service is canonically a
# setuptools, stdlib-only project (see pyproject.toml — no [tool.uv]
# section, no dependencies). Committing uv.lock would imply uv is the
# project's package manager, which it is not.
/services/orchestrator-service/uv.lock

